history.content: Happy Friday Everyone, We have a few reader positions left in EE for this coming Fall, most of them for 6 hours per week. We are looking for students who have taken these courses and received a B+ or better. If you're interested, please send me an e-mail at heather@berkeley.edu and submit an application here if you haven't applied for any Fall GSI, tutor or readership positions. Positions are available in EE 105, C128, 130, 137A, 221A, and EECS C106A and 151/251A. Thank you! Heather Levien
history.subject: A few reader positions still available in EE for Fall 2019
